    <h1>Featured Snippet</h1>
    <p class="description">The boxed answer Google shows above organic results — <strong>position zero</strong>. Appears in roughly 12% of queries and captures about <strong>8% of all clicks</strong>. Now feeds AI Overviews too.</p>
